<div>
    
    <h3>Hi <%= user.name %>,</h3>

    <p> You recently requested to reset the password of your account. Click the button below to set a new password.</p>

    <button style="background-color: rgb(226, 64, 64); padding: 10px; border: none; border-radius: 3px;">
        <a style="color: white; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;" href='<%= reset_url %>'>
            Reset your password
        </a>
    </button>
    
    <p>This link is valid for the next 10 minutes. </p>

    <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email and your password will not be changed.</p>


    Thank you.


</div>